USAGE
    ./my_rpg [-h]

BLIND JUMP
    - The map, the monsters, the chest, the player position and teleporter
    position are generated procedurally.
    - The goal is to reach the stage 5 to complete the story, than you will be
    able to play infinite mode.
    - You can save and load at any time 3 players.
    - You can loot by opening the chests.
    - Your stats will augment when you level up and by equipping new gears.
    - Find the teleporter to go to the next stage.
    - At stage 5 you have to kill 40 enemies to be able to use the teleporter.
    - A tutorial will tell you how to play when you launch a new game, you can
    skip any chatbox by pressing enter.